name: NSPersistentCloudKitContainer.EventType
desc: The type of event in a persistent CloudKit container, either setup, import, or export.

items.name: case setup
items.desc: An event the persistent CloudKit container generates when setting up a store.

items.name: case `import`
items.desc: An event the persistent CloudKit container generates when importing records into a store.

items.name: case export
items.desc: An event the persistent CloudKit container generates when exporting managed objects from a store.
